&lt;p&gt;· Experiment with generative AI technologies (LLMs, embeddings, prompt engineering, RAG, agentic workflows)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Support fine-tuning, optimisation, and evaluation of AI models&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Develop reusable AI components and microservices&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Engineering &amp;amp; Preparation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Collect, clean, and transform datasets for training and inference&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Perform exploratory data analysis to uncover patterns and insights&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Document data assumptions, limitations, and preprocessing logic&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Solution Engineering&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Contribute to AI solution design, model selection, architecture discussions, and implementation approaches&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Integrate AI models into applications, APIs, and automation workflows&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Build proof-of-concepts (POCs) and accelerate client adoption of AI&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Testing, Deployment &amp;amp; Delivery&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Conduct model validation, scenario testing, and UAT with internal and client stakeholders&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Support deployment of AI models on cloud platforms (AWS/GCP/Azure) or containerised environments&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;· Monitor performance and support continuous improvement post-deployment&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaboration &amp;amp; Consulting Exposure&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
