&lt;li&gt;Perform variance analysis and provide actionable recommendations to improve financial performance and efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive the month-end and year-end closing process, ensuring timely and accurate reporting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage relationships with external auditors, tax advisors, banks, and other financial partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyse financial data and trends to support executive decision-making and business planning.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monitor cash flow, working capital, and funding requirements to ensure sustainability and resilience as we scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
