&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate training records and assist in preparing reports on participation and learning outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the maintenance of learning databases and shared resources.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with procurement and logistics of training materials, kits, and equipment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
