&lt;li&gt;Support communication and engagement efforts to promote learning initiatives across the company.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Gather participant feedback and suggest improvements to enhance the effectiveness of programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Projects &amp;amp; Continuous Improvement&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the improvement of L&amp;amp;D workflows, templates, and documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the People team on ad-hoc HR and engagement projects related to learning and capability development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
